    <h2>üß† Course Objective</h2>
    <p>This course introduces students to information systems through real-world business cases. Students will understand how businesses utilize technology effectively to innovate, manage data, and gain competitive advantage.</p>

    <h2>üìö Teaching Methods</h2>
